* _Dynamical pattern formation in a low-concentration magnetorheological fluid under two orthogonal sinusoidal fields_ LD Yépez, JL Carrillo, F Donado, JM Sausedo-Solorio, et.al., Journal of Magnetism and Magnetic Materials 408, 321-329,	2016
* _Multifractality in dilute magnetorheological fluids under an oscillating magnetic field_, RE Moctezuma, JL Arauz-Lara, F Donado, Physical Review E 90 (6), 062303, 2014
