* _Phenomenological model for yield stress based on the distribution of chain lengths in a dilute magnetorheological fluid under an oscillatory magnetic field_, F Donado, P Miranda-Romagnoli, R Agustín-Serrano, Revista mexicana de física 59 (2), 131-140  , 2013
* _Structural transformations in magnetorheological slurries induced by perturbations_, EM de la Calleja Mora, JL Carrillo, ME Mendoza, F Donado
The European Physical Journal B 86 (4), 126, 2013
